Nigerian actress, Eniola Badmus says she pray Nigeria becomes as fine as Dubai. She wrote: “Dubai is fine shaaaaa……..I pray my” Speaking via her official Instagram page on Friday, 24th January, Badmus further gushed about the middle East country by exclaiming; ‘Dubai is fine shaaa.’ The screen diva and friend, Funke Akindele have been holidaying in Dubai in the last few weeks. See her post: Dubai is fine shaaaaa……..I pray my country can be like Dubai A post shared by  ENIOLABADMUS On Snapchat 🇳🇬 (@eniola_badmus) on Jan 24, 2020 at 4:05am PST Source